{"tid":782301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★金錢問題困擾 80後 IFC墮樓死亡","createTime":"2018-08-16T15:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T11:50:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0310fa085d50de3e162c94ff9e791df84212718f","tid":782301,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:17:17.000Z","msg":"中環國際金融中心2期發生墮樓事件，下午5時許，一名姓鄭(37歲)男子被發現從上址高處墮下，跌落民祥街東行方向的士站對埋的玻璃簷篷位置，重創昏迷，不省人事。消防接報到場升起升降台，將男事主救下，交由救護員急救，可惜證實死亡。警方封鎖現場調查，相信鄭從4樓平台墮下，現場未檢獲遺書，相信他因金錢問題不開心尋死，案件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180816/bkn-20180816173210909-0816_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180816%2Fbkn-20180816173210909-0816_00822_001.html&d=vXIrtQr4zSkx1uc2bfDxFwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a531da0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180816/bkn-20180816173210909-0816_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0d7015c7193d61f11b2f953363af1ee9b52f8648","tid":782301,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"700/2382/175/2018/...................................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwhich stock?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52889c4e8b3c7f55a30b5cc879c87a3a7e541aa","tid":782301,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"4樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係天台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18942ff8c25306574fa04f513f1b86d022023a6","tid":782301,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d7015c7193d61f11b2f953363af1ee9b52f8648","tid":782301,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"700/2382/175/2018/...................................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwhich stock?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmo